2005-07-05  Katsumi Yamaoka  <yamaoka@jpl.org>

	* shimbun/sb-mainichi.el (shimbun-mainichi-prepare-article):
	Shorten paragraph separators in the kinji articles even if they
	aren't appeared in the eye.kinji group; break continuous lines in
	the yoroku articles even if they aren't appeared in the eye.yoroku
	group.

