	Search Beta.

2005-06-28  TSUCHIYA Masatoshi  <tsuchiya@namazu.org>

	* shimbun/nnshimbun.el: Changes to support an ephemeral group.
	(TOPLEVEL): Add autoloads for `gnus-group-prefixed-name' and
	`gnus-kill-ephemeral-group'.
	(nnshimbun-group-prefixed-name): Accept an optional argument,
	`server'.
	(nnshimbun-group-ephemeral-p): Use the above function.
	(nnshimbun-request-group): Ignore `dont-check' argument when
	requesting an ephemeral group.
	(nnshimbun-close-group): Close a NOV buffer for an ephemeral
	group.
	(gnus-group-make-shimbun-group): Use a prefixed name as an
	ephemeral group.  Kill an ephemeral group before making it an
	ordinary group.

