	shimbun-header-insert-and-buffer-string.

	* shimbun/sb-pcweb-column.el: Don't inherit shimbun-text, which
	was mis-applied and ineffective.

	* shimbun/sb-sankei.el (shimbun-clear-contents): Use
	shimbun-content-start instead of shimbun-content-start-internal.

	* shimbun/sb-tdiary.el: Don't inherit shimbun-text, which was mis-
	applied and ineffective.
	(shimbun-make-contents): Use shimbun-content-start instead of
	shimbun-content-start-internal; use shimbun-content-end instead of
	shimbun-content-end-internal.

	* shimbun/sb-welt-de.el (shimbun-clear-contents): Use
	shimbun-content-start instead of shimbun-content-start-internal.

	* shimbun/sb-x51.el (shimbun-x51-prepare-article): Use
	shimbun-content-start instead of shimbun-content-start-internal;
	use shimbun-content-end instead of shimbun-content-end-internal.

	* shimbun/sb-yahoo-auctions.el (shimbun-make-contents): Use
	shimbun-content-start instead of shimbun-content-start-internal;
	use shimbun-content-end instead of shimbun-content-end-internal.

	* shimbun/sb-yahoo-sports.el: Don't inherit shimbun-text, which
	was mis-applied and ineffective.

	* shimbun/sb-yahoo.el (shimbun-yahoo-prefer-text-plain): Default
	to nil so as to generate html articles as before.

	* shimbun/sb-zeit-de.el (shimbun-make-contents): Use
	shimbun-content-start instead of shimbun-content-start-internal;
	use shimbun-content-end instead of shimbun-content-end-internal.

	* shimbun/(sb-cnet-jp.el, sb-emacswiki.el, sb-excite.el,
