2005-05-24  Katsumi Yamaoka  <yamaoka@jpl.org>

	* shimbun/sb-asahi-html.el: Don't require shimbun.
	(shimbun-asahi-html-prefer-text-plain): New constant.
	(shimbun-asahi-html-content-start): Move to sb-asahi.el.
	(shimbun-asahi-html-content-end): Ditto.
	(shimbun-make-contents): Remove.

