2005-05-20  Katsumi Yamaoka  <yamaoka@jpl.org>

	* shimbun/sb-yomiuri.el (shimbun-yomiuri-group-table): Rewrite;
	replace business with atmoney; replace culture with entertainment.
	(shimbun-index-url): Allow absolute url.
	(shimbun-yomiuri-japanese-string-to-number): Redefine it as a
	normal function.
	(shimbun-yomiuri-shorten-brackets-in-string): Abolish.
	(shimbun-yomiuri-get-top-header): New function.
	(shimbun-yomiuri-get-headers): Rewrite.
	(shimbun-yomiuri-prepare-article): Rewrite.

	* w3m.el (w3m-menubar): Add the "Close Other Sessions" button.
	(w3m-delete-other-buffers): Run w3m-force-window-update.

