2005-04-07  Katsumi Yamaoka  <yamaoka@jpl.org>

	* shimbun/sb-rss.el (shimbun-rss-compatible-encoding-alist): New
	variable.
	(shimbun-rss-get-encoding): Return a compatible encoding according
	to shimbun-rss-compatible-encoding-alist.
