	function.
	(shimbun-mime-boundary-counter): New internal variable.
	(shimbun-mime-make-multipart-message): New function.
	(shimbun-mime-retrieve-images): Likewise.
	(shimbun-make-mime-article): Rewritten to use the above functions.

