	* w3m.el (w3m-open-all-links-in-new-session): New function.
	Suggested by Yoichi NAKAYAMA <yoichi@geiin.org>.
	(w3m-view-this-url-new-session): Call
	`w3m-open-all-links-in-new-session' if the region is active.

