	(install-ja): Made it install only Japanese info.
	(install-lisp): Use `$(srcdir)/' instead of `./'.
	(install-icons): Ditto.
	(install-info-en): New rule.
	(Makefile): Use `$(srcdir)/' instead of `./'.
	(config.status): Ditto.
	(very-slow): Specify an absolute path to attic/addpath.el.

