	* w3m-cookie.el (w3m-cookie): New command.
	(w3m-about-cookie): Do nothing if w3m-use-cookies is nil.

	* w3m.el (toplevel): Added autoload setting for w3m-about-cookie;
	Added autoload setting for w3m-cookie.

